*1983 : ''Delhi: A Portrait'', Delhi Tourist Development Corporation / Oxford University Press.
*1984 : ''The Sikhs'', [[New Delhi]], Lustre Press.
*1985 : ''Indira Gandhi'' (avec Pupul Jayakar), [[New Delhi]], Lustre Press.
*1986 : 
